// Apartment layout engine
// Progressive inherited topology solver with constructive room-level and volumetric passes.
// This file keeps the allocation-readiness substrate and adds actual dwelling-unit room layout generation,
// polygon-kernel exactification hooks, curved/radial canonicalization hooks,
// and bounded 3D coupling outputs rather than adding evaluation wrappers only.

#![allow(dead_code)]
#![allow(clippy::too_many_arguments)]
#![allow(clippy::large_enum_variant)]
#![allow(unused_assignments)]
#![allow(unused_variables)]
#![allow(non_snake_case)]

