/* =============================================================================
Opening-aware apartment layout engine
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
What this layer adds:
1. Adds opening-aware topology:
   - door-node life-safety proxy
   - window-eligible frontage proxy
2. Adds vertical-access topology:
   - stair/core/elevator/shaft summaries
3. Adds roof/site/open-space packs:
   - roof constructor summary
   - site exterior / parking / landscape / open-space summaries
4. Adds yield-envelope governor:
   - FAR / DU cap / height / open-space trade-offs
5. Adds material-topology bias:
   - construction type now directly biases topology summaries
============================================================================= */

