/* =============================================================================
Progressive solve extension
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
What this extension adds:
1. Introduces an explicit pass orchestrator P0-P10.
2. Adds trigger-based selective refinement instead of whole-project exactification.
3. Adds confidence / uncertainty / stopping decisions.
4. Adds representative floor + representative unit-class solving.
5. Adds dirty-region recompute and hotspot-only 3D refinement.
6. Keeps room-synthesis semantics but deepens solve strategy, not just evaluation bundles.
============================================================================= */

#[derive(Debug, Clone)]
